name: Fragments from The Cross, Vol. 2 - Release announcement
description: @1x1_NFT are delighted to announce that "Fragments from The Cross, Vol. 2", the collaboration between Jules Maxwell (Dead Can Dance, Lisa Gerrard) and guitarist Stevie J Jones (Brian Eno, AIR, David Holmes, Craig Armstrong, Imogen Heap etc) will be released at 4pm UK time on 9th April 2021. This NFT is a limited edition of 100. Collectors of Vol.1 - be sure to check this NFT after release of Vol. 2 :)
